Class KeyDeserializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.KeyDeserializer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DurationKeyDeserializer, InstantKeyDeserializer, KeyDeserializer.None, LocalDateKeyDeserializer, LocalDateTimeKeyDeserializer, LocalTimeKeyDeserializer, MonthDayKeyDeserializer, OffsetDateTimeKeyDeserializer, OffsetTimeKeyDeserializer, PeriodKeyDeserializer, StdKeyDeserializer, YearKeyDeserializer, YearMonthKeyDeserializer, ZonedDateTimeKeyDeserializer, ZoneIdKeyDeserializer, ZoneOffsetKeyDeserializer
    public abstract class KeyDeserializer
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that defines API used for deserializing JSON content field names into Java Map keys. These deserializers are only used if the Map key class is not String or Object.
